net.kuujo.vertigo.cluster.data

Interface AsyncMultiMap<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The map key type.
    V - The map value type.

    public interface AsyncMultiMap<K,V>
    Asynchronous multi-map.

    If the current Vert.x instance is a Hazelcast clustered instance, the map will be backed by a Hazelcast map. Otherwise, the map will be backed by a Vert.x shared data map.

    Author:
    Jordan Halterman
